        "title": "Tell HN: OpenAI has started putting ads on paid programs",
        "link": "https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48673194",
        "description": "<p>I was on the £6.99/month program-- mainly because I didnt use it much. Last few days I've started seeing ads:<p>1. Ad for Financial Times\n2. Add for Shein\n3. Add for Amazon prime day<p>All 3 were on a chat where I was asking about tips on a mobile game.<p>Needless to say, I cancelled my plan. Im not paying money to see ads</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Comments URL: <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48673194\">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48673194</a></p>\n<p>Points: 22</p>\n<p># Comments: 11</p>",
